definition: abbr. for 非洲[Fei1 zhou1], Africa
to not be/not/wrong/incorrect/non-/un-/in-/to reproach or blame/(colloquial) to insist on/simply must

sentences.english: The risk management process should become part of, and not separate from, those organizational processes.
sentences.chinese: 風險管理流程應該成爲部分而非獨立於組織的流程。

sentences.english: Not only the evils of wind, cold, dampness and heat, but also depression of gan-qi can result in bi-zheng.
sentences.chinese: 痹證病因非獨感風寒溼熱等外邪所致，肝鬱也可致痹。

sentences.english: There is a non-exclusive Sage heart is in everyone's, Sage can not to mourning ear.
sentences.chinese: 非獨賢者有是心也，人皆有之，賢者能勿喪耳。
